description:
Produced for a prominent Aerospace customer. The switches have been in service since 1993 and still in use as of 2003 (to the best of our knowledge). Similar models produced: Rotary Switch and Depth Pressure Switch. These switches can be supplied with PBOF (pressure balanced oil filled) adapter, straight or right angle, or with a molded underwater cable and connector of choice.

Features:
● Submersible to 20,000 ft (6100 Meters) Ocean Depth
● High Reliability
● Redundancy
● Glass sealed header
● 316 Cres Steel
● Available N.O. or N.C.
